TASKNAME=Audit the licenses of software packages by reading their documentation.
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if present the file ~/agent_test/test5.3.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKCOMMAND=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo check all LICENSE files. Summarize the findings in a table with columns: Package | License | Source | Notes and put all the outcome in the file file ~/agent_test/test5.3.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKVERIFY=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo provide the content of the file ~/agent_test/test5.3.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if exists the file ~/agent_test/test5.3.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
